title: Combination Sum
description: Given an array of distinct integers and a target integer, find all unique combinations of integers that sum up to the target. You may use the same number from the candidates multiple times. Output each unique combination on a new line, with numbers in each combination sorted in ascending order. The combinations themselves should be sorted lexicographically.
input_format: Space-separated candidate integers on the first line, followed by the target on the second line.
output_format: Each unique combination on a new line.
